# Ownership is the governance model for this marketplace. Two tiers:
#
#   Autonomy for updates    — the owning team reviews changes to its own plugin.
#   Governance for additions — adding a plugin necessarily edits marketplace.json,
#                              which pulls in platform engineering automatically.
#
# CODEOWNERS is last-match-wins, so a PR touching only plugins/foo/** needs just
# @<org>/foo-team, while a PR adding a plugin also touches the registry below and
# therefore requires platform engineering too. No extra process needed.
#
# TODO(setup): replace @<org>/platform-eng with the real team slug before relying on
# this. GitHub SILENTLY IGNORES owners it cannot resolve — an unresolvable team makes
# governance look configured while enforcing nothing. Until real teams exist, use a
# concrete username (e.g. @stdroniv).
#
# Requires branch protection with "Require review from Code Owners" enabled.

*                                   @<org>/platform-eng

# --- Governance for additions: platform engineering ---------------------------
/.claude-plugin/marketplace.json    @<org>/platform-eng
/.github/                           @<org>/platform-eng
/scripts/                           @<org>/platform-eng
/site/                              @<org>/platform-eng
/tests/                             @<org>/platform-eng
/CONTRIBUTING.md                    @<org>/platform-eng
/SECURITY.md                        @<org>/platform-eng
/docs/                              @<org>/platform-eng

# --- Autonomy for updates: one line per plugin, added as plugins land ---------
# The linter fails any plugin without an owner here.
#
# /plugins/<name>/                  @<org>/<owning-team>
#
# NOTE: these use a concrete username per the TODO above — @<org>/platform-eng does not
# resolve yet, and an unresolvable owner enforces nothing while looking like it does.
# Swap to real team slugs once they exist.

/plugins/sdd-engineering/           @stdroniv
/plugins/research-tools/            @stdroniv
/plugins/architecture-review/       @stdroniv
/plugins/engineering-paved-path/    @stdroniv
